title: File:Wreck of Cabo de Santa Maria, 2010 December - 4.jpg
author: Ximonic (Simo Räsänen)
description: The ship wreck of Cabo de Santa Maria in Boa Vista, Cape Verde in 2010 December. The name of the ship is Cabo Santa Maria and it was wrecked here in 1968. The beach is called Praia de Atalanta after a Scandinavian ship called the Atalanta that was lost in the area in 1920.
